You talk too much, Junkers.

188
00:15:20,980 --> 00:15:23,320
Johann! Don't do this!

189
00:15:23,880 --> 00:15:26,600
Mr. Junkers doesn't know your identity, but I do!

190
00:15:27,040 --> 00:15:28,580
I was your attending physician!

191
00:15:31,220 --> 00:15:35,040
You are Johann Liebert, the elder of fraternal twins.

192
00:15:36,200 --> 00:15:39,900
You are the son of Michael Liebert, former advisor of commerce,

193
00:15:40,340 --> 00:15:44,680
