194
00:15:44,680 --> 00:15:49,120
If we know this much about you, you can't possibly escape.

195
00:15:49,700 --> 00:15:51,400
Don't add to your crimes, Johan.

196
00:15:52,800 --> 00:15:53,620
Johan, huh?

197
00:15:54,520 --> 00:15:57,140
Yes, there was a time when I went by that name.

198
00:15:58,920 --> 00:16:00,560
But you know something, Doctor?

199
00:16:00,920 --> 00:16:02,640
Johan isn't my real name.

200
00:16:02,980 --> 00:16:04,620
Wh-what are you talking about?

201
00:16:05,840 --> 00:16:08,280
You must never know about my past.

202
00:16:09,120 --> 00:16:10,520
Not about those four couples.

203
00:16:11,260 --> 00:16:12,280
Nor the Lieberts.

204
00:16:14,680 --> 00:16:16,360
But you're different, Doctor.

205
00:16:17,340 --> 00:16:20,160
You cared for me and you restored me to life.

206
00:16:20,940 --> 00:16:23,920
So I feel as though you're like a father to me.

207
00:16:24,120 --> 00:16:25,700
